<item>
            <title>[SYNAPSE-1011] Fault sequence is not get triggered when an exception comes to AbstractListMediator</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-1011</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Sample scenario:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;API:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&amp;lt;api xmlns=&quot;http://ws.apache.org/ns/synapse&quot; name=&quot;API_3&quot; context=&quot;/payments&quot;&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;resource uri-template=&quot;/edit&quot; methods=&quot;PUT POST&quot;&amp;gt;
        &amp;lt;inSequence&amp;gt;
             &amp;lt;log level=&quot;full&quot;/&amp;gt;
             &amp;lt;drop/&amp;gt;
        &amp;lt;/inSequence&amp;gt;
        &amp;lt;faultSequence&amp;gt;
            &amp;lt;log level=&quot;custom&quot;&amp;gt;
                &amp;lt;property name=&quot;state&quot; value=&quot;inside fault&quot;/&amp;gt;
            &amp;lt;/log&amp;gt;
            &amp;lt;drop/&amp;gt;
        &amp;lt;/faultSequence&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;/resource&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;/api&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Sending POST request to: &lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:8280/payments/edit&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://localhost:8280/payments/edit&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
With payload:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&amp;lt;a&amp;gt;a&amp;amp;aa&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Expected behavior is, fault sequence of API should be triggered as payload contains invalid characters.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
